test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x740345dd6100>([-56])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x740345dd6100> = [[1], [1, -56], [-56, 1], [-56, 1, -56], [1], [1, -56], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -8 == -56
 +  where -8 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -2, -4])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
